{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·003.1", "text_original": "燕燕于飛，差池其羽，之子于歸，遠送于野，瞻望弗及，泣涕如雨。", "text_normalized": "燕燕于飛，差池其羽，之子于歸，遠送于野，瞻望弗及，泣涕如雨。", "notes": "燕燕 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·003.2", "text_original": "燕燕于飛，頡之頏之，之子于歸，遠于將之，瞻望弗及，佇立以泣。", "text_normalized": "燕燕于飛，頡之頏之，之子于歸，遠于將之，瞻望弗及，佇立以泣。", "notes": "燕燕 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·003.3", "text_original": "燕燕于飛，下上其音，之子于歸，遠送于南，瞻望弗及，實勞我心。", "text_normalized": "燕燕于飛，下上其音，之子于歸，遠送于南，瞻望弗及，實勞我心。", "notes": "燕燕 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·003.4", "text_original": "仲氏任只，其心塞淵，終溫且惠，淑慎其身，先君之思，以勗寡人。", "text_normalized": "仲氏任只，其心塞淵，終溫且惠，淑慎其身，先君之思，以勗寡人。", "notes": "燕燕 Chinese stanza 4."}
